node.text: Sushi lovers raise your hand up! 🙋🏻‍♀️🙋🏻‍♂️ My customer requested for a sushi design with these Japanese words and this is what I came up with 🥰🍣🍙 I’m thinking... how about sushi pins next? 🤔
